effect_entries.effect: User switches position on the field with the friendly Pokémon opposite it.  If the user is in the middle position in a triple battle, or there are no other friendly Pokémon, this move will fail.
effect_entries.short_effect: User switches places with the friendly Pokémon opposite it.
